Notes: CHAMPIONSHIP GAME OF THE 2004 NJCU GOTHIC KNIGHT TIP-OFF TOURNAMENT.
Oneonta State wins 2004 Gothic Knight Tip-Off Tournament
From NJCU, Latrese McNair and Arnese Goodman selected to All-Tournament team.
OSC's Ann Marie Faia is Most Oustanding Player; Kristen Wittig is All-Tourney.
Game.Officials: Bob Hatler,  Tom Decker,  Courtney Cozart
